				<description><![CDATA[With the level of competition intensifying with each passing day, it is becoming increasingly difficult for the business marketing personnel to fulfill the targets, rather requirements of qualified lead generation. The outbound telemarketing campaigns are the best business strategy for the purpose. However, incessant promotional calls have had adverse impact on the productivity of the [&#8230;]]]></description>
								<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a rel="&quot;lightbox&quot;&quot;" href="http://www.fusionbposervices.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/success.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-4576" title="qualified lead generation" src="http://www.fusionbposervices.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/success-300x249.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="249" srcset="https://www.fusionbposervices.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/success-300x249.jpg 300w, https://www.fusionbposervices.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/success.jpg 323w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a>With the level of competition intensifying with each passing day, it is becoming increasingly difficult for the business marketing personnel to fulfill the targets, rather requirements of <strong><a title="qualified lead generation" href="http://www.fusionbposervices.com/lead-generation.html">qualified lead generation</a></strong>. The outbound telemarketing campaigns are the best business strategy for the purpose. However, incessant promotional calls have had adverse impact on the productivity of the telemarketing campaigns. Result? Adequate amount of qualified business leads could not be produced.</p>
<p>The business firms, rather the sales lead generation companies had to make up for the loss. So they came up with the new technique of email marketing. This technique is pretty economic; it is faster and has a wider reach. If conducted with the required meticulousness complements the efforts that are put in through the telemarketing campaigns. Here are a few guidelines to ensure that this new type of marketing campaign fetches the desired results. All call centers must adhere to these guidelines if they want to experience the maximum benefits of email marketing.</p>
<p>The subject line should be really appealing. Every person having an email account receives hundreds of emails every day, if not more. These promotional emails need to be appealing if they have to catch the attention of the target audience. Without a catchy subject, the target would not even bother to open the email and go through it.</p>
<p>Coming to the email body, the content needs to be unique, yet informative. The product or the service that is to be marketed should be described in detail; the description has to be engaging. Besides it is advised that the mail should contain a brief overview of the company and should also commit for a very pleasing business-buyer relationship. Another point of concern is that the emails should reach the inbox and not the spam folder.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
